br />\n否則你比人殺下就知點解德國係邪惡<br />\n唔洗上child登開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76002f0a0c026940f4d4b11f4580c7fa8a44fe16","tid":764770,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aca60808fee6036bd651fc6188454804ff53bc63","tid":764770,"uid":117762,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"咪弱智child登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔好懶係眾人皆醉我獨醒咁講乜點解魏國係邪惡之類<br />\n二戰納粹德國大量屠殺平民<br />\n同戰爭無關既人都慘遭毒手<br />\n再者 所有種族 色族人都有生存既權利<br />\n冇人天生係註定比人屠殺<br />\n你只係好彩遲幾十年出世<br />\n否則你比人殺下就知點解德國係邪惡<br />\n唔洗上child登開post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"關於後者 我認同所有人係自身生存不受威脅時 都唔應該損害其他人既生存權利<br />\n<br />\n但前者 二戰係總體戰 成個國家都係戰爭機器 每個人都有直接或間接參與<br />\n無同戰爭無關既人<br />\n我唔係暗示緊啲平民因爲咁而可以被殺 我都認同好多無辜平民被迫參與戰爭<br />\n但「同戰爭無關既人」係一個fail既term"},{"pid":"49a0ac68a5b43693e86fbb9eee834be71fbc12f8","tid":764770,"uid":53524,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DjgoCG6XsAEtdRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjgoCG6XsAEtdRL.jpg&h=364b8923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日正值Warsaw Uprising周年紀念"},{"pid":"b3cd6a17569e0d155688344eaf8bdc783a9e2501","tid":764770,"uid":38620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"因為先撩者賤?<br />\n兩日搞掂左個波蘭<br />\n明明講好唔打俄佬 跟住走去挑機"},{"pid":"a96b41268501a20730879b2906f5ed4b6d5e49e5","tid":764770,"uid":185884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5a7e9e3ad960c52790ccbdf8bd7123dbad19412","tid":764770,"uid":70760,